{"tid":282852,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［代開］[求救]當有女想收你做兵可以點做","createTime":"2017-06-13T16:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T16:05:14.000Z","uid":28041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74e9bdeaafaa8f6b72d06ae46a1891ec28ad7b76","tid":282852,"uid":28041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"利申先 幫朋友開 我的朋友不是我 純粹因為條女都知我朋友ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的 嗰個女仔已經有男朋友 據我所知佢哋拍咗拖兩年 <br />\n感情應該唔錯<br />\n然而 嗰個女仔係我返暑期工識到嘅 大家都啱啱考完DSE<br />\n呢度先係重點 佢做好多明顯嘅動作想我收兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如我飲過杯水 佢又會拎黎飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我食過嘅嘢 佢又會拎黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay off又會WhatsApp你兩句<br />\n佢返工又會暗示吓 好想去飲酒<br />\n問一啲事無大小嘅嘢 我覺得佢係想做個效果 等我記起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時見佢男朋友柒吓柒吓咁<br />\n真係想把心一橫去溝佢<br />\n但係我好清楚 絕對唔可以咁做<br />\n我一咁樣做 就中佢計<br />\n誠意問吓各位巴打可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c1be3ab9ed962a4869b51a38bfaba16739e174","tid":282852,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想食咪唔好理佢囉"},{"pid":"3f235498cfd230f783e333e9a6408dc62ce9aa92","tid":282852,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:43:55.000Z","msg":"溝佢"},{"pid":"5e9a50b0a192b63306ac4acb0cdaef3609c64fce","tid":282852,"uid":44798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b08834770dbeebb8f95a9912b7425f7f5b7c2614","tid":282852,"uid":44798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:50:09.000Z","msg"